pan asian music festival elegant gathering i arts at stanford university presented by sica home search this site arts enews subscribe calendar pan asian music festival elegant gathering i friday february 3 2012 12 00pm campbell recital hall free lectures and demonstrations associated with the eighth annual pan asian music festival take the format of elegant gatherings an ancient term used to describe a gathering of scholars and artists join masters yuan sha ji aeri and kazue sawai in an exploration of the history of asian instruments including the gu zheng koto and gayageum followed by a korean tea ceremony performed by experts in the tradition plus students from korea's inje university elegant gatherings also take place on 2 10 and 2 11 sponsored by department of music click for more information home calendar gallery news visiting artists grants organizations facilities plan a visit about sica students faculty staff make a gift volunteer login press sitemap contact connect twitter facebook vimeo flickr 2011 stanford university all rights reserved local user login
